{"tid":1719241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"急！抗爭之形象管理, 選舉工程：","createTime":"2019-11-14T05:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T23:00:01.000Z","uid":339469,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"37c1cd426163f2a566fa1ab1aa626a222203c524","tid":1719241,"uid":339469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:01:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">急！抗爭之形象管理, 選舉工程：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n依幾日來回中大, 沿路聽到好多auntie uncle討論依幾日嘅三罷<br />\n- 依班人有藍有黃<br />\n- 總括尼講, 佢地會擔心堵路, 爛路面社區設施會阻到部份人士, 特別係老人家, 殘疾人士&hellip;擔心佢地出唔到去睇病etc<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n情緒高漲嘅手足們睇到依到應該就會話: 阻膠, 依家係救香港等等.<br />\n但係冷靜啲先! 依篇嘢唔係話你地, 係針對<span style=\"color: blue;\">非前線和理非</span>, 罷工又冇嘢做個啲. 前線要繼續加油, 繼續做就得.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n番正題, 前線手足做嘢難免阻到上面所講嘅人士, 為免令淺黃/淺藍對我地嘅印象惡化, 小弟愚見非前線手足依家係應該要做好人, 尤其區議員選舉在即, 十分需要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保番啲形象, 同埋拉票</span></span></strong>！ <br />\n<br />\n我地要做番個樣: 唔係淨係有破壞冇建設, 例如話: 主要行人路嘅磚被搬走左啲話就幫幫手砌條簡單嘅路, 扶阿婆過磚陣馬路etc 係提供幫忙之中, 再滲番啲黃色思想俾佢地, 叫大家1124投票, sell下人選等等. 依啲行動比起貼文宣可能效果更佳.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(建制班x樣最中意做依啲嘢, 我地唔可以輸, 俾佢地搶走啲(單純嘅)auntie uncle嘅票.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n諗左少少可行嘅方案, 但好需要大家嘅幫手:<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 交通組<br />\n- 交通站提供交通資訊俾市民, 有咩港鐵站封左, 有咩車可以搭, 馬路邊到塞等等. (講埋邊到有防暴, 叫佢地小心啲.)<br />\n- 為有需要人士尋求義載 (只限睇病, 急需去醫院, 長者家屬探老人家&hellip;) (話要番工嘅有禮貌地請佢搭最塞嘅巴士路線, 介紹冤枉路即可)<br />\n- 扶阿婆過馬路交通小隊: 唔係做長期交通指揮, 但見到長者, 殘疾人士, 小朋友等等要過馬路就過去幫手stop 一stop啲車行.<br />\n<br />\n2. 物資組<br />\n- 小型物資站/上門送物資 <br />\n- 提供物資俾有需要人士, 居民 (民居戰區需要教育埋居民小心tg入屋, 同點處理)<br />\n- 上門送物資俾有需要人士, 如獨居長者.<br />\n*有需要人士, 請自行判斷, 可以係被圍困嘅學府人士.<br />\n<br />\n3. 清潔組<br />\n- 清理街道雜物, 集中雜物於一點 (堆哂去近rb位置) (我地係清理街道雜物, 唔係方便前線set rb架)<br />\n- 洗下街, 清除tg有害物質 (要大大隻字寫明/大大聲講出尼)<br />\n- 有主要行人通道, 多阿婆個啲, 整理/砌番一條簡易通道<br />\n<br />\n**每個站/小隊都要帶備文宣.<br />\n<br />\n好多人有好多因素唔可以出尼做前線, 小弟好不幸係其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 但想同所有前線人士講, 我地都會做嘢, 兄弟爬山各自努力! 所以係依度好想招攬一大班做唔到前線嘅人員, 和理非幫幫小弟一齊搞依個計劃, 小弟係自己一支公搞, <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">需要大量人士幫手</span></span> (會用google form gather大家做admin/義工, 再開tg group, 有心嘅請填寫google form)<br />\nGoogle form: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdKk52AkdDUW67X9uOlBXQjTu57R1AEvkHRZgCxritftsEcxg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdKk52AkdDUW67X9uOlBXQjTu57R1AEvkHRZgCxritftsEcxg%2Fviewform&d=7CNMK8%2FfTiCK2iXV1c%2BwrGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=08bf1c59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdKk52AkdDUW67X9uOlBXQjTu57R1AEvkHRZgCxritftsEcxg/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n暫定日子: gather夠人手即刻開始至11月24日 (11月24日後再決定是否繼續)<br />\n時間: 朝早,下晝, 夜晚<br />\n地區: 有人肯做admin就會開<br />\n(各區都需要幾名admin, 如現時社區已有類似組織, 會同佢地合作/pass俾佢地)<br />\n<br />\n區議員/社區現有組織如要協助亦請在google form填寫資料"},{"pid":"1528ef7eb1e9f114124182a56d6d72eff216230a","tid":1719241,"uid":339469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:01:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52cafe560c8d37a50fffaae834e7d08b091b32e3","tid":1719241,"uid":184455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"民宣真係好有用"},{"pid":"114f9ecf02a0b026caac4b3e109c4b7c0349ec8d","tid":1719241,"uid":339469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9212c7e8ebe6e308f1d617d47e2ae16127eddfe5","tid":1719241,"uid":339469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52cafe560c8d37a50fffaae834e7d08b091b32e3","tid":1719241,"uid":184455,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"民宣真係好有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:33:38.000Z","msg":"幫手推ahhhhh"},{"pid":"55f0233bcd1fec78ee4fd3d5fda75d73baccff0c","tid":1719241,"uid":339505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:47:25.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"3fae8fe247acd977c10050c9563b363c3bf79c10","tid":1719241,"uid":3862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:08:45.000Z","msg":"支持你，和理非唔怕比人拉"},{"pid":"ff246b3a04d93c90bde055775d6fa8e9470fb268","tid":1719241,"uid":339469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4dbd840df60ed7a432012e146e15b10b5d3cf6d4","tid":1719241,"uid":339469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:48:46.000Z","msg":"幫推！！"},{"pid":"a09dcbebe7ad399920ff72b3b3346e3f30f16c8b","tid":1719241,"uid":339469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"唔好要我p牌仔自推咁耐呀呀呀呀"},{"pid":"871c76efab85acb2d021326a8887688b194235cb","tid":1719241,"uid":289010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:49:39.000Z","msg":"文宣係有用，但得字，唔夠<br />\n我地有歌，係爭套記錄片，解釋返97後政府點樣仆街法，因為真係重有好多港豬唔知政府有咩暴政，呢段片需要好多人手，我四圍去搵，但重未有人理我"},{"pid":"5cda6cea32ebdd3bb9b320dabbc95cb2e9ee9268","tid":1719241,"uid":308355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:51:36.000Z","msg":"中共最怕選舉<br />\n佢地點都會令選舉無法舉行<br />\n手足唔好中計 中圈套被得逞<br />\n民意表一切<br />\n 變相公投"},{"pid":"639575c77b591ce9f979c1841cbf27f776b64b6a","tid":1719241,"uid":339469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5cda6cea32ebdd3bb9b320dabbc95cb2e9ee9268","tid":1719241,"uid":308355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:51:36.000Z","msg":"中共最怕選舉<br />\n佢地點都會令選舉無法舉行<br />\n手足唔好中計 中圈套被得逞<br />\n民意表一切<br />\n 變相公投"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"「我地要做番個樣: 唔係淨係有破壞冇建設」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔止係適用於區選, 前線一直做醜人, 都要有人做好人至得架. 我地要武力升級, 就要有番backup行動.</span></span><br />\n有新聞: 民建聯研組織社區義工隊安全情況下助居民清除路障<br />\n我地唔可以俾佢地爭取多左無知愛和平嘅市民民意架.<br />\n仲有係, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">透過依啲社區活動, 滲透番政權, 黑警問題俾cctvb嘅觀眾聽</span></span>"},{"pid":"1f5a6c5dbf9939c622999380778f3fb5b429f31f","tid":1719241,"uid":46822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:29:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"efb77a29db275a770212298c37d93953829985e9","tid":1719241,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0ae8738723316c06b59db5f592f836e42c9564","tid":1719241,"uid":46822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6621ebe82806905cc6a3555105ed66cc93ae2ecd","tid":1719241,"uid":38928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:52:14.000Z","msg":"推 和勇一齊救香港！"},{"pid":"0c18531a9551220ae6890584c749d93a266c2403","tid":1719241,"uid":339469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6621ebe82806905cc6a3555105ed66cc93ae2ecd","tid":1719241,"uid":38928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:52:14.000Z","msg":"推 和勇一齊救香港！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:55:54.000Z","msg":"對對對 和勇connect先係皇道<br />\n幫我推爆佢！！！！"},{"pid":"9b26bacb83677a4100e2d831ab2189c740092edd","tid":1719241,"uid":106666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:10:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c999300bec3f091b5d993e84f74d44dc8153fbad","tid":1719241,"uid":339469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-